{"tid":2147983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗稱港澳律師考試後可在大灣區就民事商業案供服務","createTime":"2020-08-09T15:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T19:01:28.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"616fef376426695fabec993b79fe0dd829f9c375","tid":2147983,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗稱港澳律師考試後可在大灣區就民事商業案供服務<br />\n2020-08-09 HKT 20:52<br />\n<br />\n&quot;人大常委譚耀宗說，港澳律師需要通過內地的考試，就可以到大灣區為內地的民事及商業案件提供法律服務，試驗期為3年。他又指，有關議案蘊釀多時，中小型律師行協會及全國人大代表早年已提出，並非突然出現。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542738-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542738-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=f63bf3ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542738-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3d560735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542738-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">事務律師都可緊緊擁抱大灣區機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a48715d3b7ce61208bccd74051ed30e4346027b0","tid":2147983,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21929d2944f36e5ebc3aca48d6ab45461b31305e","tid":2147983,"uid":156652,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.diydoutu.com/make/gif/20200809/SYTC4188499519542.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.diydoutu.com%2Fmake%2Fgif%2F20200809%2FSYTC4188499519542.gif&h=2411da5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c11360064e659ac1f57e63b8b13dd00add80305",